_sText:
Thank you for downloading my map :)

Gun Game Map Spyro (gg_spyro)

Slots: 30

Have fun :)



How to install:

copy file gg_spyro.bsp in:

...\Steam\SteamApps\Your Steam account name\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

Example:

C:\Steam\SteamApps\Your Steam account name\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

if you find a bug or problem, please contact me.

Rate and comment. :)
